  <TR><TD BGCOLOR="#add8ff" WIDTH="150"><B>Analysis</B></TD></TR>
  <TR><TD ALIGN="left" WIDTH="150">Having determined that the transaction<BR ALIGN='left'/>represented a statutory reorganization<BR ALIGN='left'/>within the purview of section 112 (g)<BR ALIGN='left'/>(1) (D), it follows that the petitioners<BR ALIGN='left'/>received the Chandler stock, as<BR ALIGN='left'/>contended by respondent, in a tax-free<BR ALIGN='left'/>exchange under section 112 (b) (3).[2]</TD></TR>
