  <TR><TD ALIGN="left" WIDTH="150">We have held that the distribution of<BR ALIGN='left'/>the $149,000 to Sponge-Aire stockholders<BR ALIGN='left'/>was essentially equivalent to the<BR ALIGN='left'/>distribution of a taxable dividend. We<BR ALIGN='left'/>think this holding is justified under<BR ALIGN='left'/>the facts disclosed by the record.</TD></TR>
